data.description: BUILDER AYDEN MODEL IN ORANGE BLOSSOM HILLS. This is the Ayden, a J&J Design Builders 2017 Parade of Homes winner. Gorgeous home was used as custom builder's model for 2 years with so many added upgrades. Appliances upgraded recently. Side entry garage on a corner lot, gives you a great setting on this nice sized lot. Soaring 9'4" ceilings throughout, crown molding with trey ceiling in the great room and master bedroom. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining. Upgraded solid wood soft-close cabinets, granite counters, some furnishings are negotiable. Upgraded 8"x36" porcelain wood-look tile flooring in main living area, gorgeous custom tile in showers, screened back porch. Right next to The Villages No required HOA.
